    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant Description
      BROTLI
      It will use one of the following Brotli compression output streams, whichever is available first: com.aayushatharva.brotli4j.encoder.BrotliOutputStream com.nixxcode.jvmbrotli.enc.BrotliOutputStream
      DEFLATE
      It will use DeflaterOutputStream as compression output stream.
      GZIP
      It will use GZIPOutputStream as compression output stream.
